description: This Chainlink VRF top 9% rating Gatinho purrs with a rating of 71, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 142, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, 1 for East, Stringalong for South, and 2 for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/50712-11722-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
